catList: This is the first course in our series of programming courses which aims at introducing the students to fundamentals of computer programming in Java. Students will learn algorithmic thinking along with the basic concepts of coding such as data types, control structures, objects, arrays and functions. This is a non-credit course with a pass/fail type grading.
